org.cpsolver.exam.model

Class ExamRoomPlacement

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.exam.model.ExamRoomPlacement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<ExamRoomPlacement>

    public class ExamRoomPlacement
extends Object
implements Comparable<ExamRoomPlacement>
    Representation of a room placement of an exam. It contains a room ExamRoom and a penalty associated with a placement of an exam into the given room.

    Version:
    ExamTT 1.3 (Examination Timetabling)
